Durban - Shocking video footage of the storm damage that swept through Durban is being circulated on social media. So far 21 people have lost their lives, the eThekwini Municipality confirmed on Tuesday morning. An additional 32 patients are being treated in hospital for various injuries and over 2000 emergency calls were logged on Monday night. Rescue operations are still underway as the city ramped up mop up operations. To view this video please enable JavaScript, and consider upgrading to a web browser that
